item.title: Website Revamp
item.description: Before/After of Homepage The header banner at the top of the old site looked clunky and amateurish. I made an upper nav ribbon with the contact information as actual clickable link text rather than an image of text. The way the homepage is now sectioned now makes it easy for a potential customer to browse/scroll and get an impression of the client that builds confidence. ×Close Before/After of Product Page The "
